sequenceDiagram
    participant TC as ToolCall
    participant E as Evaluator
    participant Calc as TrustCalculator
    participant H as HistoryStore (Redis)
    participant P as ProfileStore (Redis)
    participant S1 as ViolationRate
    participant S2 as ToolNovelty
    participant S3 as ScopeDrift
    participant S4 as ParamEntropy
    participant S5 as TimeDecay
    participant S6 as ChainDepth
    participant S7 as SessionVelocity

    TC->>E: evaluate(event)
    E->>E: policy evaluation
    E->>Calc: calculate(trust_input)
    Calc->>H: get_history(spiffe_id)
    H-->>Calc: history[] (sorted set)
    Calc->>P: get_profile(spiffe_id, agent_class)
    P-->>Calc: profile{}
    par Compute 7 signals
        Calc->>S1: compute(input, history, profile)
        Calc->>S2: compute(input, history, profile)
        Calc->>S3: compute(input, history, profile)
        Calc->>S4: compute(input, history, profile)
        Calc->>S5: compute(input, history, profile)
        Calc->>S6: compute(input, history, profile)
        Calc->>S7: compute(input, history, profile)
    end
    Calc->>Calc: weighted_sum(signals)
    Calc->>Calc: categorize(score)
    Note over Calc: Fire-and-forget persist
    Calc-->>E: TrustResult
    E->>E: low trust? override to escalate
    E-->>TC: PolicyDecision + trust
